      "content": "i get that but i really dont want to deal with the whole doctor thing right now, it takes ages to get an appointment and i just want to feel more like myself. do you think it's okay if i just stop the sertraline tomorrow and start a high dose of the st johns wort right away? like, if the herb is natural, shouldn't it just take over for the meds without any big issues?",
